name: David Tice
text: Honestly, I've never been inside. But i've definitely driven by it a couple of times. Looks pretty nice from the outside. Lots of cop cars around it all the time, so it's either really shady or really safe. I would give it a 5/5 but based on everything I hear about jails, I'm just gonna aim for the middle. Ya feel?

name: Jim Schultz
text: Absolutely pathetic! The A/C has been “broken” for at least a month now. Really?!? Exactly where are my tax dollars going?!? You’re too cheap to turn on the A/C. Why are people sleeping on the ground? Didn’t my tax dollars just go to this huge and ongoing renovation and addition? Why are you not distributing medication that inmates are required to take...like blood pressure medication? You deserve zero stars and we as a community expect and require that you treat these people in a civilized way. This will be brought up and addressed to the mayor and governor, who I both know personally. Your unethical behavior is about to come to a screeching halt!
